    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AstroBrawl is a <strong>fast-paced interplanetary shooter</strong> in which gravity is your best ally and your worst enemy. Be an alien warrior through couch/online deathmatch and survival modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3736e6644f188ebe515f3e25a706ed5a.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3736e6644f188ebe515f3e25a706ed5a.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3736e6644f188ebe515f3e25a706ed5a.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏹 Gravity: Use the planets' gravitational forces to strategically guide your projectiles through space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3eb9441b2ccb777af5347a8638779e20.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3eb9441b2ccb777af5347a8638779e20.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/3eb9441b2ccb777af5347a8638779e20.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 Versatile Arsenal: Unleash chaos with a variety of weapons and power up's, including bows, rocket launchers, shockwaves, optic camouflage, triple shots,  and even your own body for dashing and stomping. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/920a9769aedc5c5b5ad0c423737ed306.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/920a9769aedc5c5b5ad0c423737ed306.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/920a9769aedc5c5b5ad0c423737ed306.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/ab225e450aa8d73544aee89522887980.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/ab225e450aa8d73544aee89522887980.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/ab225e450aa8d73544aee89522887980.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💪 Parry mechanics: Why not?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/97a4478647a3df4c834ba1be2352ce5a.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/97a4478647a3df4c834ba1be2352ce5a.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/97a4478647a3df4c834ba1be2352ce5a.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 Interactive Environments: Explore diverse galaxies, each with its own unique characteristics. Planets can also explode affecting the whole system of forces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/f35d053adb5fcb97cca483647597f211.poster.avif?t=1740146481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/f35d053adb5fcb97cca483647597f211.webm?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/f35d053adb5fcb97cca483647597f211.mp4?t=1740146481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Couch/Online gameplay: Enjoy deathmatches and our new survival mode packed with 100 enemy waves. Think you can beat it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Cross-Platform: AstroBrawl supports both PC and Android, allowing you to challenge friends across different devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare for fast-paced interplanetary combat, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play ASTROBRAWL Now!</strong></p>",
